Q4 Should I put TO BE CPD CRM in the CRM box? yes (this is short courses for short term students so don't surface in the myUWE portal NB some short course students can transition to enrolled students)
Q5 Is there a Student Mentoring System? Is careerhub used?
Q6 Is there a pastoral care system?
Q7 what is the BB portal environment - does it come with BB?
